data.description: Absolutely adorable "updated" 4-sided brick cottage! Located within minutes of downtown Monroe. Enter the front door into the cozy, comfortable family room. Off the family room you'll find a screened in porch/sunroom that's perfect for early morning coffee and a book. New hardwood flooring in both the kitchen and dining area. Refinished hardwoods throughout the rest of the home. New blinds have been added throughout the home. The kitchen has new granite countertops with updated cabinets and hardware. Off the kitchen is the dining area complete with shiplap and a laundry room with sliding door. Two bedrooms and a bath complete this adorable home! From the back door you exit onto an oversized deck and private yard, great for entertaining and grilling, or just hanging out in the evenings. Close to Hwy 78 and all that downtown Monroe offers!
